	<name>Design</name>
	<summary>2D CAD for GNOME</summary>
	<description>
		<p>Design is a 2D computer aided design application (CAD), 
		created to meet the needs of makers and designers, 
		hobbyists and professionals that require a first class CAD application.</p>
		<p>Features:</p>
		<ul>
		<li>Supports the industry standard DXF format</li>
		<li>Uses common CAD workflows, commands and canvas management</li>
		<li>Drawing creation and manipulation using commandline or toolbar input</li>
		<li>Layer management and manipulation</li>
		<li>Entity interogation and modification </li>
	  </ul>
	</description>
